data.name: Layered Jello Shots
data.quickTastyDescription: Fun and colorful layered jello shots that are perfect for parties!
detailedCookingInstructions: Boil 1 cup of water and mix with one box of gelatin powder until fully dissolved.
Add 1/2 cup of cold water and 1/3 cup of vodka (or desired alcohol) to the mixture.
Pour a small amount (about 1/4 of the cup) into each plastic shot cup and refrigerate until set (about 1-2 hours).
Repeat with the next flavor of gelatin, making sure to wait until the previous layer is set before pouring the next.
Continue layering different flavors until the cups are full.
Once all layers are set, serve chilled and enjoy!
